column5: Walleye, Bass & Perch fishing contest at the Grand Island Rod & Gun Club Saturday.  Kevin and I got first place Walleye.  Started early Saturday fishing for Walleye.Our big fish was 30", with seven walleye over 27".  While we were trolling we got a  perch on a dipsy diver and got second place on Perch!  Dipsy divers 90' back and leadcore seven colors with worm harnesses were the hot ticket.  We had our 12 fish limit in three hours.  Great day........
Real nice!!!! congrats on the win  .
Outstanding Doug & congrats, you've been on fire this year !!
Congrats boys, some giant walleyes right there!!!
Good job.  Those perch must be a hell of a fight on a dipsy setup.
Hey congrat's to the both of you!!!  Has Kevin overcome his fear of moving water now?  LOL!
thank's to all it's been an awesome year on erie 102 walleye's in 6 trip's
